 📊 Sales Performance Analysis Dashboard

 📌 Project Overview
This project analyzes sales performance data using SQL and Power BI to generate business insights and visualize key performance metrics.

 🎯 Objective
- Analyze total sales revenue
- Identify top-performing products
- Evaluate regional sales performance
- Track monthly growth trends
- Detect high-value customers

 🛠 Tools Used
- SQL (Data Cleaning & Analysis)
- Microsoft Excel (Data Source)
- Power BI (Dashboard & Visualization)
- GitHub (Project Hosting)

 📊 Key KPIs
- Total Revenue
- Total Orders
- Average Order Value
- Top Product by Revenue
- Sales by Region
- Monthly Sales Trend

 📂 Files Included
- sales_data.xlsx
- sales_analysis.sql
- Sales_Performance_Dashboard.pbix

 📈 Dashboard Features
- Interactive filters
- Region-wise analysis
- Monthly trend analysis
- Product performance breakdown

 💡 Business Insights
This dashboard helps stakeholders:
- Make data-driven decisions
- Identify revenue growth opportunities
- Optimize product strategy
- Improve regional performance


